description:
This ropes and anchor ring will be on high rotation in your everyday jewellery collection.  A classic piece and an essential for any wardrobe. Team it with the Ropes and Anchors silver plated necklace if you like a bit of matchy-matchy.

19mm & 21mm

21mm face: 25mm

name: Anchored Necklace
description:
Gold plated single rectangle chain necklace with Rust and Regret branded tag.

There’s comfort in the familiar. It’s like an old magic trick, you have seen it before but you still love it every time you see it. To us, the anchor is an ode to loved ones, a symbol of stability and a reminder to stay grounded even on stormy seas. 

Pendant measurements: 46mm by 36mm

Chian length: 84cm

name: The Chain of Destiny Bracelet
description:
This real silver plated chain bracelet is a great addition to our range. It features a red rope end with metal hook to secure it into place. The metal hook also has our R&R logo engraved on ether side.

Measurements: 22cm from end to end.

name: The Stacker Necklace
description:
Single rectangle chain at the top with colour stacked wooden beads around the bottom

This necklace is perfect for stacking with any of our other piece. It has 5 different wooden coloured beads with an R&R logo plate on the bottom. This necklace is also real gold plated to go with all the other R&R range.

Pendant measurements: 19mm

Chain length: 84cm

name: The Ram-Snake Necklace
description:
Gold plated single chain necklace with Rust and Regret branded tag.

The majestic, serpent-horned ram pendant is a unique piece of solid hardware that commands attention. Wear it alone as an epic conversation starter or team it with another R&R gold plated necklace for extra awesome.

Pendant measurement: 45mm by 26mm

Chain length: 84cm

name: The Barbaric the 2nd
description:

name: The King of Pharaohs Necklace
description:
Gold plated, single chain necklace with Rust and Regret branded tag.

The detail on this Egyptian-inspired necklace is pharaoh-nomenal (yep, we went there). The undead pharaoh is the king of the Nile and in his time the ruler of the lands. Wear it accordingly

Pendant measurement: 30cmm & 3mm thick

Chain length: 84cm

name: Ropes & Anchors Necklace
description:
Silver plated single chain necklace with Rust and Regret branded tag.

This ropes and anchor coin necklace will be on high rotation in your everyday jewellery collection.  A classic piece and an essential for any wardrobe. Team it with the Ropes and Anchors gold plated ring if you like a bit of matchy-matchy.

Pendant measurement: 22mm

name: The Skull Necklace
description:
Black stone beaded necklace with Rust and Regret branded tag at the top.

We wanted to add a little colour to our range so what better way then to add some pastel skulls. Stand out from the rest with the aqua painted metal skull pendant

Pendant measurements: 30mm

Chain length: 84cm

name: The Rapahael Necklace
description:
Black stone beaded necklace with Rust and Regret branded tag.

This awesome necklace was named after one of our friends Glenn - legend, and leopard print enthusiast! The real gold plating on this number will only add to this cat's swagger. 

Note: this shape has been a point of contention, with some mistaking it for some kind of anti religion statement thanks to misinformed goths and death metal bands. It is actually based on an inverted Latin cross, otherwise known as St. Peter's Cross - and the pope himself has one carved in his chair. Know your symbology, people!

Pendant measurements: 42mm by 22mm

Chain length: 84cm
